{"type":"message","id":"c18c9c9b","parentId":"9d51939d","timestamp":"2026-06-07T05:36:55.035Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_77n8hphpxmm0_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ReCAPTCHA\n    recaptcha_SearxEngineCaptcha: 604800\n\n  # remove format to deny access, use lower case.\n  # formats: [html, csv, json, rss]\n  formats:\n    - html\n\nserver:\n  # Is overwritten by ${SEARXNG_PORT} and ${SEARXNG_BIND_ADDRESS}\n  port: 8888\n  bind_address: \"127.0.0.1\"\n  # public URL of the instance, to ensure correct inbound links. Is overwritten\n  # by ${SEARXNG_BASE_URL}.\n  base_url: false  # \"http://example.com/location\"\n  # rate limit the number of request on the instance, block some bots."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":116,"aggregated":"# ReCAPTCHA\n    recaptcha_SearxEngineCaptcha: 604800\n\n  # remove format to deny access, use lower case.\n  # formats: [html, csv, json, rss]\n  formats:\n    - html\n\nserver:\n  # Is overwritten by ${SEARXNG_PORT} and ${SEARXNG_BIND_ADDRESS}\n  port: 8888\n  bind_address: \"127.0.0.1\"\n  # public URL of the instance, to ensure correct inbound links. Is overwritten\n  # by ${SEARXNG_BASE_URL}.\n  base_url: false  # \"http://example.com/location\"\n  # rate limit the number of request on the instance, block some bots.","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780810615028}}
{"type":"message","id":"10bcee9c","parentId":"c18c9c9b","timestamp":"2026-06-07T05:37:05.685Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了。配置里 `formats: [html]`，所以 JSON 格式被禁用了，返回 403。\n\n现在用户问\"可以吗？\"——我应该简短回答：可以，然后把方案讲清楚。这是修改配置，按 SOUL.md 的规则要先确认。但用户已经说\"可以吗\"，说明在问我意见。\n\n回答：\n1. 问题根因：settings.yml 里 formats 只允许 html，json 被禁了 → 403\n2. 解决方案：把 json 加进 formats\n3. 改完要重启 SearXNG 容器才生效\n\n直接给方案，等用户拍板。","thinkingSignature":"e7684b289c88a76f231b2cd469b3764d97c986128156e49079669a2810379f63"},{"type":"text","text":"可以。根因找到了：\n\n**问题**：`settings.yml` 第 85-87 行，`formats` 只配了 `html`，没开 `json`，所以 API 接口 `format=json` 直接 403。\n\n**修法**（一行改动 + 重启）：\n\n```yaml\nformats:\n  - html\n  - json\n```\n\n然后：\n\n```bash\ndocker restart searxng\n```\n\n重启后我再跑一次 search.py 验证。改的是你宿主机的 `~/searxng-data/settings.yml`（bind 挂载到容器内 `/etc/searxng`），改完容器内立即生效。\n\n要我直接动手改吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":188,"output":260,"cacheRead":56562,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57010,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780810615061,"responseId":"06743677ef41d06dae7b71ac7ac29f5a"}}
