{"type":"message","id":"70e154d4","parentId":"d9659ec5","timestamp":"2026-06-07T05:38:39.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文件 owner 是 UID 977（docker 容器内的某个用户），不在我（UID 1000）的写权限范围里。我又不能 sudo 免密。\n\n这是 Docker bind mount 的典型问题：容器内的 root 写出的文件，宿主机这边是 977 拥有。\n\n但我可以用 docker exec 直接改容器内的文件！\n\n策略：\n1. `docker exec -u root searxng sed -i '...'` 直接改容器内的 /etc/searxng/settings.yml\n2. 容器内的修改会通过 bind mount 反映到宿主机文件\n3. 然后 docker restart searxng\n\n这样最干净。\n\n或者用 `docker cp` 把文件复制出来修改再复制进去。\n\n或者最简单：`docker exec` 直接 sed。\n\n让我执行。","thinkingSignature":"5a6844789319a7ea6cf8b658bcee09580ff0e7a7161f713d859244b78f5d9e61"},{"type":"text","text":"文件 owner 是 docker 容器用户（UID 977），我直接写不了。换个思路：**进容器里改**。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eur932y57hpu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker exec -u root searxng sed -i '/^  formats:/,/^    - /{s/^    - html$/    - html\\n    - json/}' /etc/searxng/settings.yml\necho \"---改完后容器内：---\"\ndocker exec searxng sed -n '83,90p' /etc/searxng/settings.yml\necho \"---改完后宿主机：---\"\nsed -n '83,90p' /home/halei/searxng-data/settings.yml"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":138,"output":327,"cacheRead":58621,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59086,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780810707052,"responseId":"067436d32d0658afff5fa3ba08cfa139"}}
