{"type":"message","id":"3e5a49cc","parentId":"6df0c41f","timestamp":"2026-06-07T05:39:29.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看清楚了：\n- 设置文件里**列出了 279 个引擎**\n- 其中 28 个被标记为 `inactive: true`（被禁用）\n- 大部分**没有显式 enable 也没有 disable**——SearXNG 默认行为：未显式 `disabled: true` 的引擎是启用的\n\n但是测试返回说 `brave/duckduckgo/google/wikipedia` 都 timeout。这是**网络层**的问题——这台机器访问不到 Google/Brave/DuckDuckGo 等外网搜索引擎。\n\n但是搜索 0 结果可能是因为：\n1. 网络封禁导致 timeout\n2. 启用的引擎虽然没标 inactive，但实际全 timeout 了\n\n我需要测试一下网络情况，以及找一些国内能访问的引擎（比如 bing、baidu、sogou、360search）。","thinkingSignature":"ae2834a190e3cff17b06e40d24b0fcfc6aa7fe6bf07f5e468ee489acadf5d31c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0gkwh54k4mcc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 测试网络：能不能访问 Google/DuckDuckGo/Bing/Baidu ===\"\nfor host in \"www.google.com\" \"duckduckgo.com\" \"cn.bing.com\" \"www.baidu.com\" \"www.sogou.com\"; do\n  printf \"%-20s \" \"$host\"\n  curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" --max-time 5 \"https://$host\" 2>&1 || echo \"失败\"\ndone\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 看看设置文件里有没有像 bing/baidu/sogou 这种国内能访问的引擎 ===\"\ngrep -A 1 \"name: bing\\|name: baidu\\|name: sogou\\|name: 360search\" /home/halei/searxng-data/settings.yml | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":502,"output":372,"cacheRead":59987,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60861,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780810756510,"responseId":"06743705700b8dc396689fab2b417d2a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"55299719","parentId":"3e5a49cc","timestamp":"2026-06-07T05:39:36.370Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0gkwh54k4mcc_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 测试网络：能不能访问 Google/DuckDuckGo/Bing/Baidu ===\nwww.google.com       HTTP 000 | 2.763972s\n失败\nduckduckgo.com       HTTP 000 | 2.711972s\n失败\ncn.bing.com          HTTP 200 | 0.673345s\nwww.baidu.com        HTTP 200 | 0.174238s\nwww.sogou.com        HTTP 200 | 0.233942s\n\n=== 看看设置文件里有没有像 bing/baidu/sogou 这种国内能访问的引擎 ===\n  - name: 360search\n    engine: 360search\n--\n  - name: 360search videos\n    engine: 360search_videos\n--\n  - name: baidu\n    baidu_category: general\n--\n  - name: baidu images\n    baidu_category: images\n--\n  - name: baidu kaifa\n    baidu_category: it\n--\n  - name: bing\n    engine: bing\n--\n  - name: bing images\n    engine: bing_images"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6706,"aggregated":"=== 测试网络：能不能访问 Google/DuckDuckGo/Bing/Baidu ===\nwww.google.com       HTTP 000 | 2.763972s\n失败\nduckduckgo.com       HTTP 000 | 2.711972s\n失败\ncn.bing.com          HTTP 200 | 0.673345s\nwww.baidu.com        HTTP 200 | 0.174238s\nwww.sogou.com        HTTP 200 | 0.233942s\n\n=== 看看设置文件里有没有像 bing/baidu/sogou 这种国内能访问的引擎 ===\n  - name: 360search\n    engine: 360search\n--\n  - name: 360search videos\n    engine: 360search_videos\n--\n  - name: baidu\n    baidu_category: general\n--\n  - name: baidu images\n    baidu_category: images\n--\n  - name: baidu kaifa\n    baidu_category: it\n--\n  - name: bing\n    engine: bing\n--\n  - name: bing images\n    engine: bing_images","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780810776368}}
{"type":"message","id":"1f7d7551","parentId":"55299719","timestamp":"2026-06-07T05:39:45.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"确诊了：\n- **网络情况**：Google / DuckDuckGo 完全封死（timeout），Bing / Baidu / Sogou / 360search 国内正常\n- **解决方案**：用 `--engines bing,baidu,360search` 参数指定国内能访问的引擎\n\n让我先实测一下这几个国内引擎能不能搜到东西：","thinkingSignature":"f933316b932560725bb9152c93a20f223098935837a935d699be318008a90100"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n1wj4q5m3an1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 用国内引擎测试（bing + baidu + 360search）===\"\npython3 /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/scripts/search.py \"openclaw\" --engines \"bing,baidu,360search\" --limit 5\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 中文搜索测试 ===\"\npython3 /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/scripts/search.py \"TikTok 选品\" --engines \"bing,baidu\" --lang zh --limit 5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":260,"output":214,"cacheRead":60847,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61321,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780810776390,"responseId":"0674371940209b97b4b28a8b6bb7f941"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dacddf2c","parentId":"1f7d7551","timestamp":"2026-06-07T05:39:53.035Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n1wj4q5m3an1_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 用国内引擎测试（bing + baidu + 360search）===\n[\n  {\n    \"title\": \"OpenClaw — Personal AI Assistant\",\n    \"url\": \"https://openclaw.ai/\",\n    \"content\": \"OpenClaw — The AI that actually does things. Your personal assistant on any platform. ... OpenClaw The AI that actually does things. Clears your inbox, sends emails, manages your ...\",\n    \"engine\": \"360search\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"OpenClaw 龙虾零成本快速安装教程,不用花钱,无须 API Key...\",\n    \"url\": \"https://github.com/mqyqingfeng/AI-Blog/issues/1\",\n    \"content\": \"1. 安装 OpenClaw 的官网是:https://openclaw.ai/,在首页提供了安装命令: #macOS/Linuxcurl -fsSL https://openclaw.ai/install.sh|bash#Windowspowershell -c\\\"irm https://openclaw.ai/install.ps1 | iex\\\" 运行命令后,会检测安装环境,注意需要 Node v22 及以上版本。 2. 设置 然后进入设置阶段: 2.1 ...\",\n    \"engine\": \"baidu\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"OpenClaw - OpenClaw\",\n    \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/zh-CN\",\n    \"content\": \"OpenClaw 是一个 自托管 Gateway 网关，它把你常用的聊天应用和渠道界面（包括内置渠道，以及 Discord、Google Chat、iMessage、Matrix、Microsoft Teams、Signal、Slack、Telegram …\",\n    \"engine\": \"bing\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Openclaw - 百家号\",\n    \"url\": \"https://author.baidu.com/home/1839966473109034\",\n    \"content\": \"Openclaw 实在智能是一家专注于人工智能与超自动化解决方案的科技公司,基于AI Agent(智能体)和自研TARS大模型技术,提供实在Agent、实在RPA数字员工等产品,助力电商、制造、医药、金融等领域企业实现数字化转型。\",\n    \"engine\": \"baidu\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"OpenClaw_360百科\",\n    \"url\": \"https://baike.so.com/doc/30561030-32448349.html\",\n    \"content\": \"OpenClaw（曾用名：Clawdbot、Moltbot），是一款开源的、本地优先的AI智能体框架，由程序员彼得·斯坦伯格（Peter Steinberger）开发，核心采用 TypeScript 编写。其标志采用“龙虾”形象，口号为 “The AI that actually does things”。OpenClaw... 详情>>发展历程 - 研发背景 - 功能服务 - 产品架构 - 全部\",\n    \"engine\": \"360search\"\n  }\n]\n\n=== 中文搜索测试 ===\n[\n  {\n    \"title\": \"TikTok 怎么选品？6个选品策略和选品工具分享\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.shoplazza.cn/blog/tiktok-product-selection\",\n    \"content\": \"TikTok 选品的关键不在“产品是否优质”,而在“是否适合在平台成交”。产品需要在短时间内抓住注意力并激发购买冲动,同时具备被算法放大的内容潜力,还要在佣金、物流与广告成本后保留合理利润空间。三者缺一不可。 在初步筛选后,应借助官方及第三方工具验证数据,再通过小批量测款判断真实表现,避免盲目备货。同时,可考虑...\",\n    \"engine\": \"bing\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"TikTok 怎么选品？TikTok Shop 选品逻辑、方法与避坑指南\",\n    \"url\": \"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2038567226773600034\",\n    \"content\": \"2026年5月15日 · 现在的 TikTok 越来越依赖“ 内容驱动成交 ”，选品逻辑与传统电商截然不同。 过去靠跟卖爆款的方法，已难再奏效。 本文将结合当前 TikTok 的市场趋势，从选品逻辑、选品方法以及选品 …\",\n    \"engine\": \"bing\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"TikTok Shop选品工具数据分析爆品发现趋势预测\",\n    \"url\": \"http://www.datacaciques.com/blog/industry/101263\",\n    \"content\": \"但可以用这些方法免费选品:1)直接刷TikTok Shop\\\"为你推荐\\\"和\\\"热卖榜单\\\"(效率低但免费);2)关注头部达人主页查看带货商品;3)使用EchoTik等工具的免费试用期(通常7-14天);4)数字酋长ERP的选品功能包含在套餐中,相当于免费(如果你本来就要用ERP)。 Q2: 如何判断一个品类是否已经饱和? 看三个指标:第一,Top 1\",\n    \"engine\": \"baidu\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"FastMoss官网-TikTok电商数据分析平台\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.fastmoss.com/zh/dashboard\",\n    \"content\": \"FastMoss工作台整合TikTok电商核心数据，覆盖达人、商品、视频、广告、直播与商家表现，多国家市场同步分析。支持ROI评估、带货趋势监测、竞品对比与运营决策辅助，帮助跨境商家快速掌握市场 …\",\n    \"engine\": \"bing\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"TikTok 怎么选品?TikTok Shop 选品逻辑、方法与避坑指南\",\n    \"url\": \"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1865168092567234755&wfr=spider&for=pc\",\n    \"content\": \"因此，现在做 TikTok 选品，更重要的是选择真正适合 TikTok 内容传播逻辑的产品，才能实现长期运营。二、TikTok选品的底层逻辑了解完选品逻辑再进行选品，才可能事半功倍！选品逻辑主要分为以下三个层面：1. TikTok用户行为逻辑： 内容触发购买，不是搜索匹配需求 TikTok 用户打开 App 一般不是为了购物，而是为了刷视频...\",\n    \"engine\": \"baidu\"\n  }\n]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6816,"aggregated":"=== 用国内引擎测试（bing + baidu + 360search）===\n[\n  {\n    \"title\": \"OpenClaw — Personal AI Assistant\",\n    \"url\": \"https://openclaw.ai/\",\n    \"content\": \"OpenClaw — The AI that actually does things. Your personal assistant on any platform. ... OpenClaw The AI that actu