{"type":"message","id":"e155d3e7","parentId":"722411b1","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:03:46.840Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到根因了！\n\n**问题诊断：**\n\n`openclaw.json` 的 `agents.list` 里有 10 个 agent 配置（main, tts, content, koc, traffic, ops, director, finance, review, agent-orchestrator），**配置是好的**。\n\n但 `agents_list` 工具只返回了 main 1 个 agent。\n\n**为什么？** 让我看 agents_list 的返回：\n```json\n{\n  \"requester\": \"main\",\n  \"allowAny\": false,\n  \"agents\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"main\",\n      \"configured\": true,\n      ...\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n字段是 `allowAny: false` 和 `agents: [main]`。\n\n这个工具的语义是：**返回当前 agent（requester=main）能 spawn 出哪些子 agent**。它白名单了 `agents_list` 的 agents 字段。\n\n**这是 OpenClaw 的一个安全/权限机制：默认 agent 之间的 spawn 权限是关闭的，需要明确配置才能互相 spawn。**\n\n我需要找到哪个配置项控制这个。\n\n让我搜一下：","thinkingSignature":"85e7d4af756ee65c9b92efbfbb67ea9a968cd3761f40c8c9f6d9bf9421fc6ab7"},{"type":"text","text":"找到根因了！10 个 agent 配置都在 `openclaw.json` 里，配置没问题，但 `agents_list` 的返回显示 `allowAny: false` ——**OpenClaw 默认禁止 agent 互相 spawn，需要白名单授权**。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k3q7dw3iq9zz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 找 OpenClaw 的 allow/spawn 配置 schema ===\"\npython3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    cfg = json.load(f)\ndef find(obj, keys, path=''):\n    hits = []\n    if isinstance(obj, dict):\n        for k, v in obj.items():\n            new_path = f'{path}.{k}' if path else k\n            if k in keys:\n                hits.append((new_path, v))\n            hits.extend(find(v, keys, new_path))\n    elif isinstance(obj, list):\n        for i, v in enumerate(obj):\n            hits.extend(find(v, keys, f'{path}[{i}]'))\n    return hits\nfor k in ['allowAny', 'allowSpawn', 'spawn', 'allowList', 'allow', 'allowAgents', 'allowed', 'spawning', 'subagents']:\n    hits = find(cfg, {k})\n    if hits:\n        print(f'键 \"{k}\" 出现 {len(hits)} 次:')\n        for p, v in hits[:3]:\n            print(f'  {p}: {json.dumps(v, ensure_ascii=False)[:200]}')\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":4235,"output":561,"cacheRead":69851,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74647,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780812206398,"responseId":"06743cae85fcbf796e0a977fee0e5a01"}}
{"type":"message","id":"859f1cb3","parentId":"e155d3e7","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:03:47.635Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_k3q7dw3iq9zz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 找 OpenClaw 的 allow/spawn 配置 schema ===\n键 \"allow\" 出现 1 次:\n  plugins.allow: [\"browser\", \"lossless-claw\", \"memory-core\", \"minimax\", \"openclaw-lark\", \"openclaw-weixin\", \"openrouter\", \"wecom-openclaw-plugin\", \"workboard\"]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":124,"aggregated":"=== 找 OpenClaw 的 allow/spawn 配置 schema ===\n键 \"allow\" 出现 1 次:\n  plugins.allow: [\"browser\", \"lossless-claw\", \"memory-core\", \"minimax\", \"openclaw-lark\", \"openclaw-weixin\", \"openrouter\", \"wecom-openclaw-plugin\", \"workboard\"]","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780812227630}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5831e59","parentId":"859f1cb3","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:04:00.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没找到具体的 spawn allow 配置。让我查 schema。","thinkingSignature":"59bf99bdab12634a2805752002e7c66d9717e5cc32dd0b6a6cc09eb825d16929"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1bmakkrkne76_1","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.schema.lookup","path":"agents.list[*]."}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1bmakkrkne76_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 看 main agent 配置里有没有 spawn 相关字段 ===\"\npython3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    cfg = json.load(f)\nmain_cfg = [a for a in cfg['agents']['list'] if a['id']=='main'][0]\n# 列出 main 的所有顶层 key\nprint(\"main agent 的配置 keys:\")\nfor k in main_cfg.keys():\n    print(f\"  - {k}\")\nprint()\nprint(\"全部子结构（递归）:\")\ndef walk(obj, prefix='', depth=0):\n    if depth > 3: return\n    if isinstance(obj, dict):\n        for k, v in obj.items():\n            print(f\"{'  '*depth}{prefix}{k}: {type(v).__name__}{f' = {v}' if not isinstance(v, (dict,list)) else ''}\")\n            walk(v, '', depth+1)\n    elif isinstance(obj, list) and len(obj) > 0:\n        for k in obj[0].keys() if isinstance(obj[0], dict) else []:\n            print(f\"{'  '*depth}{prefix}[0].{k}\")\nwalk(main_cfg)\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":101,"output":326,"cacheRead":74633,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75060,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780812227668,"responseId":"06743cc4fd1441a027e4506e4e05e6f8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c570c87","parentId":"a5831e59","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:04:01.152Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1bmakkrkne76_1","toolName":"gateway","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"result\": {\n    \"path\": \"agents.list.*\",\n    \"schema\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"additionalProperties\": false\n    },\n    \"reloadKind\": \"hot\",\n    \"children\": [\n      {\n        \"key\": \"id\",\n        \"path\": \"agents.list.*.id\",\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"required\": true,\n        \"hasChildren\": false,\n        \"reloadKind\": \"hot\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"key\": \"default\",\n        \"path\": \"agents.list.*.default\",\n        \"type\": \"boolean\",\n        \"required\": false,\n        \"hasChildren\": false,\n        \"reloadKind\": \"hot\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"key\": \"name\",\n        \"path\": \"agents.list.*.name\",\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"required\": false,\n        \"hasChildren\": false,\n        \"reloadKind\": \"hot\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"key\": \"description\",\n        \"path\": \"agents.list.*.description\",\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"required\": false,\n        \"hasChildren\": false,\n        \"reloadKind\": \"hot\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"key\": \"workspace\",\n        \"path\": \"agents.list.*.workspace\",\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"required\": false,\n        \"hasChildren\": false,\n        \"reloadKind\": \"hot\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"key\": \"agentDir\",\n        \"path\": \"agents.list.*.agentDir\",\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"required\": false,\n        \"hasChildren\": false,\n        \"reloadKind\": \"hot\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"key\": \"model\",\n        \"path\": \"agents.list.*.model\",\n        \"required\": false,\n        \"hasChildren\": true,\n        \"reloadKind\": \"hot\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"key\": \"models\