{"type":"message","id":"0c5ab1e6","parentId":"30289475","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:05:04.699Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_deulrei3zas8_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  Hint: commands suffixed with * have subcommands. Run <command> --help for details.\n  acp *                Run and manage ACP-backed coding agents\n  agent                Run one agent turn via the Gateway\n  agents *             Manage isolated agents (workspaces, auth, routing)\n  approvals *          Manage exec approvals (gateway or node host)\n  backup *             Create and verify local backup archives for OpenClaw\n                       state\n  capability *         Run provider capability commands (fallback alias: infer)\n  channels *           Add, remove, login, and inspect messaging channels\n---\n\nOpenClaw 2026.6.1 (2e08f0f) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents [options] [command]\n\nManage isolated agents (workspaces + auth + routing)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help    Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add           Add a new isolated agent\n  bind          Add routing bindings for an agent\n  bindings      List routing bindings\n  delete        Delete an agent and prune workspace/state\n  list          List configured agents\n  set-identity  Update an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\n  unbind        Remove routing bindings for an agent\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agents\n---\n\nOpenClaw 2026.6.1 (2e08f0f) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw config [options] [command]\n\nNon-interactive config helpers (get/set/patch/unset/file/schema/validate). Run\nwithout subcommand for guided setup.\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help           Display help for command\n  --section <section>  Configuration sections for guided setup (repeatable). Use\n                       with no subcommand. (default: [])\n\nCommands:\n  file                 Print the active config file path\n  get                  Get a config value by dot path\n  patch                Patch config from a JSON5 object in one validated write.\n                       Objects merge recursively, arrays/scalars replace, and\n                       null deletes a path.\n                       Examples:\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"brisk-harbor","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"=== 看看有没有 openclaw CLI 改 agent 的命令 ===\n\nOpenClaw 2026.6.1 (2e08f0f) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw [options] [command]\n\nOptions:\n  --container <name>   Run the CLI inside a running Podman/Docker container\n                       named <name> (default: env OPENCLAW_CONTAINER)\n  --dev                Dev profile: isolate state under ~/.openclaw-dev, default\n                       gateway port 19001, and shift derived ports\n                       (browser/canvas)\n  -h, --help           Display help for command\n  --log-level <level>  Global log level override for file + console\n                       (silent|fatal|error|warn|info|debug|trace)\n  --no-color           Disable ANSI colors\n  --profile <name>     Use a named profile (isolates\n                       OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH under\n                       ~/.openclaw-<name>)\n  -V, --version        output the version number\n\nCommands:\n  Hint: commands suffixed with * have subcommands. Run <command> --help for details.\n  acp *                Run and manage ACP-backed coding agents\n  agent                Run one agent turn via the Gateway\n  agents *             Manage isolated agents (workspaces, auth, routing)\n  approvals *          Manage exec approvals (gateway or node host)\n  backup *             Create and verify local backup archives for OpenClaw\n                       state\n  capability *         Run provider capability commands (fallback alias: infer)\n  channels *           Add, remove, login, and inspect messaging channels\n---\n\nOpenClaw 2026.6.1 (2e08f0f) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents [options] [command]\n\nManage isolated agents (workspaces + auth + routing)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help    Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add           Add a new isolated agent\n  bind          Add routing bindings for an agent\n  bindings      List routing bindings\n  delete        Delete an agent and prune workspace/state\n  list          List configured agents\n  set-identity  Update an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\n  unbind        Remove routing bindings for an agent\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agents\n---\n\nOpenClaw 2026.6.1 (2e08f0f) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw config [options] [command]\n\nNon-interactive config helpers (get/set/patch/unset/file/schema/validate). Run\nwithout subcommand for guided setup.\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help           Display help for command\n  --section <section>  Configuration sections for guided setup (repeatable). Use\n                       with no subcommand. (default: [])\n\nCommands:\n  file                 Print the active config file path\n  get                  Get a config value by dot path\n  patch                Patch config from a JSON5 object in one validated write.\n                       Objects merge recursively, arrays/scalars replace, and\n                       null deletes a path.\n                       Examples:\n","name":"echo === 看看有没有 openclaw CLI 改 agent 的命令 ==="},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780812304697}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d25abd6","parentId":"0c5ab1e6","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:05:14.203Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有直接改 subagents.allowAgents 的 CLI。但 `openclaw config get/set/patch` 应该可以改，前提是不被 protect。\n\n继续直接编辑 openclaw.json + 重启 gateway。","thinkingSignature":"e092e22dd47cb6ee1efb905b165fdd940ff6f5e157d18949e1cdd03781860229"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ny65kav8kl8t_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    cfg = json.load(f)\n\n# 找到 main 配置，添加 subagents\nfor agent in cfg['agents']['list']:\n    if agent['id'] == 'main':\n        agent['subagents'] = {\n            'allowAgents': [\n                'tts', 'content', 'koc', 'traffic', 'ops',\n                'director', 'finance', 'review', 'agent-orchestrator'\n            ],\n            'requireAgentId': True\n        }\n        print(f\"已为 main 添加 subagents 配置\")\n        break\n\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(cfg, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\n# 验证写入成功\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    cfg2 = json.load(f)\nmain_cfg = [a for a in cfg2['agents']['list'] if a['id']=='main'][0]\nprint(f\"main.subagents = {json.dumps(main_cfg.get('subagents'), ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)}\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":475,"output":323,"cacheRead":80046,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780812304728,"responseId":"06743d115a6a6e3bdb26875abca59988"}}
