{"type":"message","id":"2fdd6760","parentId":"b9e4c58c","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:23:19.733Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了：\n- `tools.agentToAgent.enabled` 是个 boolean 字段\n- `tools.agentToAgent.allow` 是允许的 target agent 白名单\n- 当前 `openclaw.json` 里 `agentToAgent` 是空 `{}`\n- 关键提示：\"**Keep disabled or tightly scoped unless cross-agent orchestration is intentionally enabled**\"——OpenClaw 设计上就默认不鼓励开这个功能\n- 另一个重要提示：\"**Use explicit allowlists to avoid uncontrolled cross-agent call graphs**\"\n\n而且 `reloadKind: \"none\"` 意味着这个改动**需要重启 gateway**（不是 hot reload）。\n\n让我直接编辑 openclaw.json，把 agentToAgent 配置加上：\n- enabled: true\n- allow: 9 个 agent 的白名单\n\n然后重启 gateway。\n\n不过等等，注意到\"allow\" 的语义是\"allowlist of target agent IDs permitted for agent_to_agent calls\"——这跟 subagents.allowAgents 是类似概念。\n\n让我配置：\n```json\n\"agentToAgent\": {\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"allow\": [\n    \"tts\", \"content\", \"koc\", \"traffic\", \"ops\",\n    \"director\", \"finance\", \"review\", \"agent-orchestrator\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n然后重启 gateway。\n\n但有一个值得讨论的点——这个改动**影响整个 gateway**（不是单 agent 的），相当于把\"agent 间通信\"的大门开了一道。按 OpenClaw 提示是默认禁用的，我开了之后需要让用户知道。\n\n而且这是一个改动安全模型的决策（allowAny/默认禁用 → 显式白名单）。这跟我之前改 main 的 subagents.allowAgents 类似但范围更大。\n\n我应该：\n1. 改配置 + 重启\n2. 但跟用户说清楚这次改动的范围\n\n不过用户已经表态\"你要解决你的 agent 内部通信问题\"——这就是授权我开这个门。\n\n直接干，然后报告。\n\n我先备份。","thinkingSignature":"5b7ccf1160dced14feed4fbcd25c2e000cad71740b644dd34e54eaba6aba5140"},{"type":"text","text":"字段确认：\n\n- `tools.agentToAgent.enabled` —— 总开关\n- `tools.agentToAgent.allow` —— target agent 白名单\n- `reloadKind: \"none\"` —— **需要重启 gateway**（不是 hot reload）\n- OpenClaw 明确提示「Keep disabled or tightly scoped unless cross-agent orchestration is intentionally enabled」\n\n我直接开。备份+改+重启："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3r8wr8hq4ua8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak-a2a-$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S)\n\npython3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    cfg = json.load(f)\n\n# 在 tools 下加 agentToAgent\nif 'tools' not in cfg:\n    cfg['tools'] = {}\ncfg['tools']['agentToAgent'] = {\n    'enabled': True,\n    'allow': [\n        'tts', 'content', 'koc', 'traffic', 'ops',\n        'director', 'finance', 'review', 'agent-orchestrator'\n    ]\n}\n\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(cfg, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\n# 验证\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    cfg2 = json.load(f)\nprint(f\"tools.agentToAgent = {json.dumps(cfg2['tools']['agentToAgent'], ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)}\")\nEOF"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3r8wr8hq4ua8_2","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"restart","delayMs":4000,"note":"启用 agent-to-agent 通信（agentToAgent.enabled=true），并配置 9 个 agent 白名单。需要重启 gateway 因为 reloadKind=none","restartDelayMs":5000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":506,"output":840,"cacheRead":87577,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88923,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780813376229,"responseId":"0674414001edb867ef7e5ad225f5b6b0"}}
