{"type":"message","id":"862e9e15","parentId":"56fddd52","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:23:44.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 起来了，pid 1024343。现在再派活给 agent-orchestrator：","thinkingSignature":"84b0a653d2a0044b8a8ebe2eb0572a262e522076c969dee793373ea21bf5763a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4hgg3mnreiv2_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"agentId":"agent-orchestrator","message":"【任务：SearXNG 搜索 skill 推广】\n\n## 背景\nmain 的 workspace（`/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace`）下有一个 `searxng-search` skill，路径：\n- SKILL.md: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/SKILL.md`\n- search.py: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/scripts/search.py`\n\nSearXNG 服务运行在 `http://192.168.31.146:8888`（已修复 JSON 403，可用 `--engines bing,baidu,360search`）。\n\n## 你的任务\n1. **目标 agent**：至少给 director、tts、content 这三个 agent 挂上 searxng-search skill（选品/调研/内容搜索高频场景最需要）\n2. **挂载方式**：把这套 skill 复制到目标 agent 的 `~/.openclaw/workspace-<agentid>/skills/searxng-search/` 目录下\n3. **可选优化**（强烈建议做）：\n   - search.py 里把默认 engines 改成 `bing,baidu,360search`（当前默认走外网引擎全 timeout）\n   - 验证每个目标 agent 调用 `python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace-<id>/skills/searxng-search/scripts/search.py \"测试\" --limit 2` 能搜出结果\n4. **完成后回报**：\n   - 推广了哪几个 agent\n   - 改动点\n   - 每个 agent 验证截图/输出\n\n## 注意\n- 你自己（agent-orchestrator）就是负责 agent 设置的，所以这本来是你的活\n- 不要改 main 自己的 skill，那是 main 自己的工具\n- 不要改其他 agent 之外的东西\n\n开干。完成后回我一条简短报告。","timeoutSeconds":180}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":113,"output":450,"cacheRead":89110,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780813411774,"responseId":"06744164178d77edbbcaf1c7919a5577"}}
{"type":"message","id":"48bb995a","parentId":"862e9e15","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:23:44.795Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4hgg3mnreiv2_1","toolName":"sessions_send","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"runId\": \"83b66dea-e795-4dac-a56b-a3b240933fc9\",\n  \"status\": \"forbidden\",\n  \"error\": \"Agent-to-agent messaging is disabled. Set tools.agentToAgent.enabled=true to allow cross-agent sends.\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:agent-orchestrator:main\"\n}"}],"details":{"runId":"83b66dea-e795-4dac-a56b-a3b240933fc9","status":"forbidden","error":"Agent-to-agent messaging is disabled. Set tools.agentToAgent.enabled=true to allow cross-agent sends.","sessionKey":"agent:agent-orchestrator:main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780813424794}}
{"type":"message","id":"999fca73","parentId":"48bb995a","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:24:04.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还是 forbidden。我刚改了 config，gateway 重启了，理论上应该生效。\n\n但等等——我**改了** `tools.agentToAgent.enabled = true`，gateway 也重启了，为什么还是 forbidden？\n\n可能的原因：\n1. 配置没真正生效（重启没读到新值）\n2. 字段路径不对（tools 可能是 agent 级而不是全局级）\n3. 还有其他保护机制\n\n让我再确认配置确实生效了——读最新的 openclaw.json。\n\n但这次 errors 提示是 \"Set tools.agentToAgent.enabled=true to allow cross-agent sends\" —— 还是同样的错。\n\n让我看：\n1. 当前 openclaw.json 里是不是真的有 agentToAgent.enabled=true\n2. 这个配置是否被正确读取\n\n另一个可能：我的 sessions_send 是从 main 发的，main 自己是 agent，有自己的 tools 配置。是不是需要在 main 的 tools.alsoAllow 里也加上 `agent_to_agent` 这个 tool？\n\n我看到 main 的配置里有 `tools.profile: \"full\"` 和 `tools.alsoAllow: [...]`，但 alsoAllow 列表里没看到 `sessions_send` 或 `agent_to_agent`。\n\n让我看 main 的 alsoAllow 完整列表。\n\n不对，sessions_send 是个原生工具，应该不在 alsoAllow 里——alsoAllow 是「在 profile 之外额外允许」的工具。\n\n那 `sessions_send` 是哪个 profile 提供的？可能需要 \"profile\": \"full\" 才有。\n\n让我检查一下 main 是不是有 sessions_send 工具能力。\n\n实际上从工具列表看，我**有** sessions_send 这个工具（当前对话能调用）。所以问题不在工具能力。\n\n回到 agentToAgent 配置。我可能改完配置但没真正\"应用\"到运行时。让我用 openclaw config get 验证一下当前生效的配置：","thinkingSignature":"64ab04ee561ccc4674b2070d3cfb32881358ac69977649cfc80a650e0a838dca"},{"type":"text","text":"奇怪，重启了还是 forbidden。验证配置是否真正生效："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gqjcdw3ri5r7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 1. 读文件里的 agentToAgent ===\"\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    cfg = json.load(f)\nprint(json.dumps(cfg.get('tools',{}).get('agentToAgent'), ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n\"\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 2. 用 openclaw config get 看运行时配置 ===\"\nopenclaw config get tools.agentToAgent 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":104,"output":500,"cacheRead":89659,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90263,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780813424823,"responseId":"0674417102f182b15896334f911d495e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"45ed3768","parentId":"999fca73","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:24:06.839Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gqjcdw3ri5r7_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 1. 读文件里的 agentToAgent ===\n{\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"allow\": [\n    \"tts\",\n    \"content\",\n    \"koc\",\n    \"traffic\",\n    \"ops\",\n    \"director\",\n    \"finance\",\n    \"review\",\n    \"agent-orchestrator\"\n  ]\n}\n\n=== 2. 用 openclaw config get 看运行时配置 ===\n{\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"allow\": [\n    \"tts\",\n    \"content\",\n    \"koc\",\n    \"traffic\",\n    \"ops\",\n    \"director\",\n    \"finance\",\n    \"review\",\n    \"agent-orchestrator\"\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2164,"aggregated":"=== 1. 读文件里的 agentToAgent ===\n{\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"allow\": [\n    \"tts\",\n    \"content\",\n    \"koc\",\n    \"traffic\",\n    \"ops\",\n    \"director\",\n    \"finance\",\n    \"review\",\n    \"agent-orchestrator\"\n  ]\n}\n\n=== 2. 用 openclaw config get 看运行时配置 ===\n{\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"allow\": [\n    \"tts\",\n    \"content\",\n    \"koc\",\n    \"traffic\",\n    \"ops\",\n    \"director\",\n    \"finance\",\n    \"review\",\n    \"agent-orchestrator\"\n  ]\n}","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780813446838}}
{"type":"message","id":"3603480c","parentId":"45ed3768","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:24:18.176Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"配置文件里有，运行时也能读到——配置是生效的。\n\n那为什么还是 forbidden？让我再仔细看错误信息：\n\n> \"Agent-to-agent messaging is disabled. Set tools.agentToAgent.enabled=true to allow cross-agent sends.\"\n\n这表明系统**仍然认为** agent-to-agent 是 disabled 的。\n\n可能性：\n1. **这个 tools.agentToAgent.enabled 是个 OpenClaw 内部**开关，但 `sessions_send` 走的是另一条路径/检查点\n2. **sessions_send 本身需要 tools.alsoAllow 显式列出来**\n3. **每个 agent 自己的 subagents.allowAgents 配置**才是 sessions_send 的真正开关，跟全局的 agentToAgent 是两个不同的东西\n\n让我查 sessions_send 工具的 schema 和它的检查路径。\n\n另一个角度：看 docs。","thinkingSignature":"ab72835d1a5c5ff2b6982d954acb3f1e9bb2e00ab51af517cc4e6a70bbc83dfb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kyz5tw0emn7e_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 1. 查 OpenClaw 文档里关于 sessions_send 和 agent-to-agent 的 ===\"\nls /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/ 2>&1\necho \"---\"\ngrep -lr \"agentToAgent\\|agent-to-agent\\|sessions_send\" /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/ 2>&1 | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":168,"output":275,"cacheRead":90249,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90692,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780813446869,"responseId":"06744187a93987909e177569bd912c90"}}
