{"type":"message","id":"56f46933","parentId":"997ea42f","timestamp":"2026-06-07T06:27:43.753Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"gateway pid 一直是 1024343，没真正重启过！\n\n这是 OpenClaw 用了**热重启信号**（SIGUSR1），让进程自己 reload 配置。但**配置没真正被读到**——可能因为 OpenClaw 缓存了旧 config，或者 SIGUSR1 走的 reload 路径不读 `tools.agentToAgent`。\n\n或者：pid 1024343 是 supervisor，supervisor 重启了 worker 但 supervisor 自己的 pid 不变。\n\n让我直接看 gateway 是不是真的在跑、还是已经挂了：","thinkingSignature":"02b1433a2add046d4c069a81139508e297350b2ac02c5acafd2f45191cb84c5c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pac6q5xilyv1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== gateway 进程树 ===\"\nps -ef | grep openclaw | grep -v grep | head -10\necho \"\"\necho \"=== gateway 端口监听 ===\"\nss -tlnp 2>&1 | grep 18789\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 用 status 命令看 gateway ===\"\nopenclaw gateway status 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":112,"output":212,"cacheRead":99339,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99663,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780813647416,"responseId":"06744250e8bd7e713185a0a973a70f6e"}}
