{"type":"message","id":"de437437","parentId":"eda96c00","timestamp":"2026-06-07T07:13:50.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"可以了吗\"——这是接着之前的工作流。让我回顾一下整个事情的进展：\n\n1. **SearXNG 修复**：✅ 完成\n   - settings.yml 加了 json format\n   - 容器重启，JSON API 通了\n   - 用 bing,baidu,360search 引擎能搜到结果\n\n2. **agent 内部通信修复**：部分完成\n   - ✅ 改 `main.subagents.allowAgents` → agents_list 列出 9 个 agent\n   - ⏳ `tools.agentToAgent.enabled=true` 配上了，但**没真正生效**——gateway 多次 restart 都 coalesced 合并了，pid 没换，配置没真正被读到\n   - 我正准备用 `systemctl --user restart` 强制重启，但**命令被 SIGTERM 中断了**\n\n3. **当前状态**：gateway 在 15:13 之前没真正重启过。systemctl 命令被 SIGTERM 杀掉。\n\n我需要：\n1. 先确认现在 gateway 状态（是不是被 systemd 重启了）\n2. 再次尝试真正重启（这次用不同方式）\n3. 然后派活给 agent-orchestrator\n\n而且时间已经从 14:27 跳到 15:13 了——过了 46 分钟。中间发生了什么？让我看看。\n\n实际上 SIGTERM 中断可能是 gateway 自己收到 SIGTERM 后，systemd 又把整个 supervisor 杀掉了。但我重启是让 systemd 处理的——SIGTERM 是 systemd 给 openclaw-gateway 发的停机信号。supervisor 收到 SIGTERM 后把状态写到 stdout 退出，然后 systemd 重新拉起。\n\n那现在 gateway 应该已经被 systemd 拉起了。让我看看进程状态。\n\n但有个关键问题：之前 main agent（我自己）也是跑在 gateway 进程下的吗？还是独立的？\n\nOpenClaw 的架构里：\n- Gateway 是 supervisor / 配置中心\n- 每个 agent session 是独立 node 进程（或者子进程）\n- 我（main）当前正在运行的 session 也是 gateway 拉起的\n\n如果 gateway 被重启了，那我的 session 也会被杀掉。但用户现在又发消息了——说明 main session 又被拉起来了？或者 gateway 重启了但我的 session 还活着？\n\n或者——systemctl 命令只是被 SIGTERM 中断，gateway 实际**没**被重启。\n\n让我先查状态。","thinkingSignature":"f0977f6795c5af235253b831b69700ddae188ada5be36fbb458eabbb5f1357be"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_09gncyh8guz5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== gateway 当前状态 ===\"\npgrep -af \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -3\necho \"\"\necho \"=== gateway 是否监听端口 ===\"\nss -tlnp 2>&1 | grep 18789 | head -2\necho \"\"\necho \"=== gateway 进程的 uptime ===\"\nPID=$(pgrep -f \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -1)\nif [ -n \"$PID\" ]; then\n  ps -o pid,etime,start,cmd -p $PID 2>&1\nfi"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":100457,"output":620,"cacheRead":1394,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102471,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780816413766,"responseId":"06744d1ecb1f9089bde41218ab7086f0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2eac059c","parentId":"de437437","timestamp":"2026-06-07T07:13:51.631Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_09gncyh8guz5_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== gateway 当前状态 ===\n1024860 /usr/bin/node /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789\n1025717 /bin/bash --noprofile --norc -c echo \"=== gateway 当前状态 ===\" pgrep -af \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -3 echo \"\" echo \"=== gateway 是否监听端口 ===\" ss -tlnp 2>&1 | grep 18789 | head -2 echo \"\" echo \"=== gateway 进程的 uptime ===\" PID=$(pgrep -f \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -1) if [ -n \"$PID\" ]; then   ps -o pid,etime,start,cmd -p $PID 2>&1 fi\n\n=== gateway 是否监听端口 ===\nLISTEN 0      511        127.0.0.1:18789      0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"node\",pid=1024860,fd=25))          \nLISTEN 0      511            [::1]:18789         [::]:*    users:((\"node\",pid=1024860,fd=26))          \n\n=== gateway 进程的 uptime ===\n    PID     ELAPSED  STARTED CMD\n1024860       45:22 14:28:28 /usr/bin/node /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":191,"aggregated":"=== gateway 当前状态 ===\n1024860 /usr/bin/node /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789\n1025717 /bin/bash --noprofile --norc -c echo \"=== gateway 当前状态 ===\" pgrep -af \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -3 echo \"\" echo \"=== gateway 是否监听端口 ===\" ss -tlnp 2>&1 | grep 18789 | head -2 echo \"\" echo \"=== gateway 进程的 uptime ===\" PID=$(pgrep -f \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -1) if [ -n \"$PID\" ]; then   ps -o pid,etime,start,cmd -p $PID 2>&1 fi\n\n=== gateway 是否监听端口 ===\nLISTEN 0      511        127.0.0.1:18789      0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"node\",pid=1024860,fd=25))          \nLISTEN 0      511            [::1]:18789         [::]:*    users:((\"node\",pid=1024860,fd=26))          \n\n=== gateway 进程的 uptime ===\n    PID     ELAPSED  STARTE