{"type":"message","id":"82a22df4","parentId":"2eac059c","timestamp":"2026-06-07T07:14:07.151Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"哦，gateway 早就重启了！新的 pid 是 1024860，uptime 45:22 分钟，14:28:28 启动。\n\n时间线：\n- 14:10:39 旧 gateway 启动 (pid 1024343)\n- 14:26:18 我改了 openclaw.json\n- 14:27:xx 我调 gateway restart，被合并没生效\n- 14:28:28 systemd 把 gateway 真正重启了 (pid 1024860) — **这次生效了**\n- 14:28:28 之后 agentToAgent.enabled=true 真正加载了\n\n那为什么之前 sessions_send 还报 forbidden？\n\n哦——14:28:28 之后，**用户的\"我手理解错了吗\"**消息之后，我调了 sessions_send — 那个时间点 agentToAgent 应该已经生效了。\n\n但 sessions_send 还是报 \"Agent-to-agent messaging is disabled\"。\n\n让我再看看是不是配置真的有问题——刚才 pid 1024343 → 1024860 的转换。openclaw.json 文件最后改的时间应该是 14:26:18。\n\n那 1024860 启动时间 14:28:28——这是在我改配置之后。它读到的应该是新配置。\n\n但 sessions_send 依然 forbidden。说明问题不是\"配置没生效\"，而是别的。\n\n让我重新细看代码：\n```js\nconst routingA2A = cfg.tools?.agentToAgent;\nconst enabled = routingA2A?.enabled === true;\n```\n\n`routingA2A?.enabled === true` —— 只有当 enabled === true 才是 true。空对象 {} 的话 enabled === undefined !== true，所以 enabled = false。\n\n我配的：\n```json\n{\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"allow\": [...]\n}\n```\n\n`enabled === true` ✓\n\n那为什么还 forbidden？让我**直接再试一次** sessions_send，看现在的结果。","thinkingSignature":"f9a60ce9a55fc3811d6b5fa0e71f9fb4cc1f1a8587cb1a1a9b8db84b8458ff77"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway 早就重启过了（pid 1024343 → 1024860，14:28:28 启动，比我改配置晚 2 分钟）。所以配置应该**已经生效**。再试一次 send，看是不是真的还没生效："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9l9tnj6fe03b_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"agentId":"agent-orchestrator","message":"【任务：SearXNG 搜索 skill 推广】\n\nmain 的 workspace（`/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace`）下有 `searxng-search` skill：\n- SKILL.md: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/SKILL.md`\n- search.py: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/scripts/search.py`\n\nSearXNG 服务 `http://192.168.31.146:8888`（已修好 JSON 403，配合 `--engines bing,baidu,360search` 搜得到结果）。\n\n请把 skill 复制到 director、tts、content 这三个 agent 的 workspace：`~/.openclaw/workspace-<id>/skills/searxng-search/`，并把 search.py 默认 engines 改成 `bing,baidu,360search`（外网引擎全 timeout）。验证每个 agent 跑 `python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace-<id>/skills/searxng-search/scripts/search.py \"测试\" --limit 2` 能搜出结果。完成后回我简短报告。","timeoutSeconds":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":335,"output":724,"cacheRead":102457,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103516,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780816431671,"responseId":"06744d305802a3ffc4c26503cf8b8e69"}}
