{"type":"message","id":"61e00f6a","parentId":"36170c54","timestamp":"2026-06-07T07:14:24.507Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"错误变了！从 \"disabled\" 变成 \"denied\"。\n\n之前：\n- \"Agent-to-agent messaging is disabled. Set tools.agentToAgent.enabled=true...\" → 说明 enabled=false\n- 现在：\n- \"Agent-to-agent messaging denied by tools.agentToAgent.allow.\" → 说明 **enabled=true 了**，但 `allow` 列表没匹配上\n\n错误信息从 \"disabled\" 变成 \"denied\"——这是**进展**！enabled 真的生效了。但 `allow` 列表没匹配上。\n\n现在 `allow` 列表里有 \"agent-orchestrator\"，但还报 \"denied\"。\n\n可能的原因：\n1. **白名单的匹配方式** —— 源码说 `compileAgentAllowPattern` 会把字符串编译成 pattern。我看代码：\n   ```js\n   const matchesAllow = (agentId) => {\n     if (allowPatterns.length === 0) return true;  // 关键：空 allow 列表 = 允许\n     ...\n   }\n   ```\n\n2. **匹配逻辑**：\n   ```js\n   const isAllowed = (requesterAgentId, targetAgentId) => {\n     if (requesterAgentId === targetAgentId) return true;\n     if (!enabled) return false;\n     return matchesAllow(requesterAgentId) && matchesAllow(targetAgentId);\n   };\n   ```\n   \n   也就是说，**requester agent 和 target agent 都必须在 allow 列表里**。\n\n3. 我**只配了 target agent 的 allow**（用户允许 main 调哪些 agent），但没把 main 自己也加进去！\n\n让我看 agent-orchestrator 收到的 runId 和 sessionKey 看看：runId=140595fc，sessionKey=\"agent:agent-orchestrator:main\"。\n\ntarget = agent-orchestrator（在我 allow 列表里 ✓）\nrequester = main（**不在 allow 列表里** ✗）\n\n所以 `matchesAllow(\"main\")` = false，导致 `isAllowed = false`，denied。\n\n修法：把 \"main\" 也加进 allow 列表。\n\n让我也加进去。\n\n另外我注意到：\"denied\" 这个错误是 `a2aDeniedMessage` 的 'send' 分支，所以是 `isAllowed(requester, target) === false`。\n\n也就是 `matchesAllow(\"main\") && matchesAllow(\"agent-orchestrator\")` 至少有一项 false。\n\n我配的 allow 是：\n```\n[\"tts\", \"content\", \"koc\", \"traffic\", \"ops\", \"director\", \"finance\", \"review\", \"agent-orchestrator\"]\n```\n\nmain 不在里面！所以 matchesAllow(\"main\") = false → denied。\n\n修法：把 \"main\" 也加进去。","thinkingSignature":"17829a134174375768b8b2e9175aa0e650c9f1e3b892e6eab7821c471b9a03e7"},{"type":"text","text":"**进展了！** 错误从 \"disabled\" 变成 \"denied\"——说明 `enabled=true` 真的生效了，但 `allow` 没匹配上。\n\n源码逻辑是 **`requester` 和 `target` 都必须在 allow 列表里**。我光把 9 个执行 agent 加进了 allow，但忘了把 **`main`（调用方）也加进去**！所以 `matchesAllow(\"main\") === false` → denied。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fhnnpwu1f1fy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo '{\"tools\":{\"agentToAgent\":{\"enabled\":true,\"allow\":[\"main\",\"tts\",\"content\",\"koc\",\"traffic\",\"ops\",\"director\",\"finance\",\"review\",\"agent-orchestrator\"]}}}' | openclaw config patch --stdin 2>&1 | tail -5\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 验证 ===\"\nopenclaw config get tools.agentToAgent 2>&1 | tail -15"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":97,"output":759,"cacheRead":103502,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104358,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780816447989,"responseId":"06744d4042d5947e424aed1963e7a4d8"}}
