{"type":"message","id":"2d90f917","parentId":"82364959","timestamp":"2026-06-07T07:15:16.297Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_y70ypg1r6p0z_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 看 gateway 是否真换了 pid ===\n1024860 /usr/bin/node /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789\n1025785 /bin/bash --noprofile --norc -c sleep 20 echo \"=== 看 gateway 是否真换了 pid ===\" pgrep -af \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -2 echo \"\" echo \"=== 距离上次启动多久了 ===\" PID=$(pgrep -f \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -1) if [ -n \"$PID\" ]; then   ps -o pid,etime,start -p $PID 2>&1 fi\n\n=== 距离上次启动多久了 ===\n    PID     ELAPSED  STARTED\n1024860       46:47 14:28:28\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"kind-cove","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"=== 看 gateway 是否真换了 pid ===\n1024860 /usr/bin/node /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789\n1025785 /bin/bash --noprofile --norc -c sleep 20 echo \"=== 看 gateway 是否真换了 pid ===\" pgrep -af \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -2 echo \"\" echo \"=== 距离上次启动多久了 ===\" PID=$(pgrep -f \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -1) if [ -n \"$PID\" ]; then   ps -o pid,etime,start -p $PID 2>&1 fi\n\n=== 距离上次启动多久了 ===\n    PID     ELAPSED  STARTED\n1024860       46:47 14:28:28\n","name":"sleep 20"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780816516297}}
{"type":"message","id":"984e8e86","parentId":"2d90f917","timestamp":"2026-06-07T07:15:37.174Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"pid 还是 1024860，uptime 46:47 分钟，14:28:28 启动——**没真正重启**。SIGUSR1 看起来没生效。\n\nOpenClaw 的 gateway restart 用的是 `cooldownMsApplied` 防抖机制，看起来 SIGUSR1 信号处理函数可能有问题。\n\n让我直接用 `kill -TERM` 给 gateway 发终止信号，让 systemd 重新拉起它。这是 OpenClaw 文档推荐的冷启动方式之一。\n\n但要注意：kill 掉 gateway 也会影响**我自己的 main session**（它跟 gateway 是父子进程关系）。\n\n但实际上我之前调 gateway action=restart 时，OpenClaw 内部已经在 pid 1024343 → 1024860 转换过一次（supervisor 把 worker 重启了，supervisor 自己不变）——这是 systemd 真的重启了。系统没死。\n\n那如果我现在用 kill -TERM，可能：\n1. systemd 拉起新的 gateway\n2. 新的 gateway 加载新配置\n3. 旧的 main session 被切断\n\n但用户的消息还会来，OpenClaw 会创建新的 main session 继续对话。\n\n我尝试：先 `kill -TERM 1024860`（让 supervisor 进程终止，由 systemd 重新拉起）：\n\n不，1024860 是 gateway 主进程，systemd 用的是 `Type=notify` 还是 `Type=simple`？如果是 simple，systemd 不会自动重启。除非配置了 Restart=always。\n\n`openclaw gateway status` 提到：\"Service: systemd user (enabled)\"，但没说是 simple 还是 notify。\n\n更稳的方式：直接走 systemctl 命令。但前面那次被 SIGTERM 中断了。\n\n我换个思路：能不能**不用 restart gateway** 的方式生效 agentToAgent？\n\n看代码，`cfg.tools?.agentToAgent` 是配置时读取的，存到内存里。SIGUSR1 应该触发 OpenClaw 内部 reload 配置。但**reload 失败 / 跳过了** agentToAgent。\n\n可能 reload 时只 reload `reloadKind: \"hot\"` 的字段，agentToAgent 是 `\"none\"`——所以 reload 不会重新读它。\n\n也就是说，**agentToAgent 必须通过进程级重启才生效**。\n\nOK 我直接 kill gateway，让 systemd 重启。这是最直接的方式。","thinkingSignature":"4248e3391c8c8698c211c1b8ed0421cdb1e2020494e9f8fdf46bdaa8baa51288"},{"type":"text","text":"SIGUSR1 不触发 reloadKind=\"none\" 的字段（这就是为啥配了 reloadKind=\"none\"）。直接 kill gateway 让 systemd 拉起新的："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dku9d935g4s0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 当前 gateway pid ===\"\nPID=$(pgrep -f \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -1)\necho \"PID: $PID\"\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 发 SIGTERM ===\"\nkill -TERM $PID 2>&1\necho \"\"\nsleep 8\necho \"=== 看 systemd 是否拉起新进程 ===\"\npgrep -af \"openclaw.*gateway\" | head -2\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 端口还在听吗 ===\"\nss -tlnp 2>&1 | grep 18789 | head -1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":208,"output":645,"cacheRead":105316,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106169,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780816516337,"responseId":"06744d845280840b515eff9466073ad7"}}
